<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    {{>layout/header}}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/evaluate.css">>
</head>
<body>
    {{>layout/nav}}

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-5 align-items-center">
            <div id="page-header" class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                <h3>해당 날씨에 입으신 지난 옷차림은 어떠셨나요?</h3>
            <!--   평가할 내용 없을 때     -->
            {{^wears}}
                <p class="mt-4">아쉽지만 아직 평가할 옷차림이 없네요...<br>
                    지난 옷차림 등록하고, 내 체감온도에 맞는 옷차림을 추천 받아보세요 <i class="far fa-smile"></i></p>
                 <a id="btn-reg" href="/users/save-wear" class="btn btn-outline-light stretched-link">등록하러 가기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
            {{/wears}}

                <p class="mt-4">평가를 해주시면, 정확한 추천에 도움이 됩니다 <i class="far fa-smile"></i><br>
                    ❌를 선택하시면, 앞으로의 평가항목에서 제외됩니다</p>
            </div>
        <div>
            {{#wears}}
            <div class="eval-list-section">
                <div class="eval row media-body pb-3 mx-2 mb-0 lh-125 rounded my-3 p-3">
                    <div class="wear_code" style="display: none">{{wear_code}}</div>
                    <!--     그 날의 옷차림       -->
                    <div class="eval-clothes my-auto col-md-4 pl-2 themed-grid-col text-center">
                        <img class="outerImg" src="" alt="OUTER">
                        <img class="topImg" src="" alt="TOP">
                        <img class="bottomImg" src="" alt="BOTTOM">
                    </div>
                    <!--      날짜      -->
                    <div class="eval-date eval-date col-md-2 themed-grid-col pt-3 border-left">
                        <span class="sub-title font-weight-light text-lg-left">날짜</span>
                        {{#wear_date}}
                        <div class="eval-date-2 eval-date-date my-auto text-monospace">{{wear_date}}</div>
                        {{/wear_date}}
                    </div>
                    <!--      기온      -->
                    <div class="eval-date col-md-2 themed-grid-col pt-3 border-left">
                        <span class="sub-title font-weight-light text-lg-left">기온</span>
                        {{#temp_code}}
                            <div class="eval-date-2 eval-date-temp my-auto text-monospace">{{temp_code}}</div>
                        {{/temp_code}}
                    </div>
                    <!--    버튼        -->
                    <div class="eval-btn col-md-4 themed-grid-col pr-1 pt-2 border-left">
                        <span class="eval-wear-no hidden">{{wear_no}}</span>
                            <button id="hot-btn" class="btn">
                                <i class="fas fa-thermometer-full"></i>
                                <p class="btn-text">더워요</p>
                            </button>
                            <button id="warm-btn" class="btn" >
                                <i class="fas fa-thermometer-half"></i>
                                <p class="btn-text">적절해요</p>
                            </button>
                            <button id="cold-btn" class="btn" >
                                <i class="fas fa-thermometer-empty"></i>
                                <p class="btn-text">추워요</p>
                            </button>
                            <button id="del-btn" class="btn">
                                <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                                <p class="btn-text mt-2">삭제</p>
                            </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/wears}}
    </div>

    <script src="/js/eval.js"></script>
    {{>layout/footer}}

</body>
</html>